- cs.DB (Databases) is another possible category as the paper mentions the suitability of the proposed system for cloud computing, which involves data storage and retrieval. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possible category as the paper discusses the complexity of the proposed algorithm. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the approximation of string matching distance, which can be viewed as an information-theoretic problem.
